    AbstractFastPreferenceData
    Abstract FastFeatureData, implementing the interfaces of FastUserIndex and FastItemIndex by delegating to implementations of these.

    Fast version of PreferenceData, where preferences for users and items are stored internally by the indexes provided by FastUserIndex and FastItemIndex.

    A user or item preference by indexes.
